pathTokens: 01. Maiden Cliff & Frostbite, Pete's & Blue Vein

content.description:
A large (400 ft) wall of rock best climbed when frozen in place!  Up and right from Frostbite Falls.  

  The current (2010) guidebook lists the following climbs (L to R):    Local Hero M6 *    Dirty Dancing M3 *   Canadian Ballet M6 *   Double Clutch  NEI 4 *   Turf Battle M3     Kiss of the Spider Woman  NEI 3, 5.8 or A1   Pete's Puzzle  NEI 3+, 5.7 R/X *    Iron Maiden  NEI 4 M4  

  Descent from the climbs either 2 rope raps from trees or there's a diagonal gully on the left.
